{"tid":226378,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載]愛上新聞女主播 陳嘉倩好pure好true！","createTime":"2017-05-02T13:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T11:27:48.000Z","uid":55603,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"852f5b2888f6a2b2921a99c5d47295cc96d7dcb5","tid":226378,"uid":55603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"原文網址：<a href=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/view1/2017/04/28/tvb-prettiest-anchor/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fview1%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2Ftvb-prettiest-anchor%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=d8a6a95c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mentalkhk.com/view1/2017/04/28/tvb-prettiest-anchor/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/18175536_10154482897842727_22256756_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F18175536_10154482897842727_22256756_o.jpg&h=a94814a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每晚打開電視，我細佬嘴角都會露出少男懷春的靦腆笑容，直到有日我忍唔住走過去拍佢個頭，問：<br />\n「你笑乜L嘢笑到發晒姣咁？」然後佢指住電視，螢光幕播映的是無綫6點半新聞，而負責報新聞的主播叫陳-嘉-倩。<br />\n<br />\n我好後悔自己對我細佬咁惡，我錯怪佢，因為自己曾經都有一排J過無綫女主播 ，咩咩周嘉儀、趙海珠真係令人心心眼、好GF-able。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由新至舊 歷代無綫新聞女主播回顧<br />\n<br />\n1. 陳嘉倩<br />\n<br />\n被網友稱呼做靜香、嘉倩bb的陳嘉倩，原來今年只得26歲，屬90後，係無綫目前最young的新聞主播。2012年陳嘉倩畢業於中文大學英文系，佢入職短短半年就兼任《周末主播室》，其後再主持《新聞提要》、《天氣報告》、《香港早晨》。<br />\n除咗學歷及工作表現睇得，最值得留意嘅係，就係佢素顏一樣省鏡，最冇得輸。<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/%E9%99%B3%E5%98%89%E5%80%A9IG-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2598%2589%25E5%2580%25A9IG-4.jpg&h=5edf3195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/%E9%99%B3%E5%98%89%E5%80%A9IG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2598%2589%25E5%2580%25A9IG.jpg&h=bb08a52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/%E9%99%B3%E5%98%89%E5%80%A9IG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2598%2589%25E5%2580%25A9IG3.jpg&h=e4fc654d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Screen-Shot-2017-04-25-at-6.46.06-PM-816x1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FScreen-Shot-2017-04-25-at-6.46.06-PM-816x1024.png&h=79d11e31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 駱文捷<br />\n<br />\n最近有唔少朋友有講起呢位新聞主播，駱文捷，不過可惜啦，佢剛剛已成為人妻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/0cdb4da4d94df8e5bacf89d63a5377c5-1024x536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F0cdb4da4d94df8e5bacf89d63a5377c5-1024x536.jpg&h=c83fd82a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/50901_20170112230048_58779a20cb16f-820x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F50901_20170112230048_58779a20cb16f-820x1024.jpg&h=22f5a71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.陳嘉欣<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉欣唔算好標青，靚到你非留意佢不可嗰種，但論工作表現，陳嘉欣算係淡定大方，感覺予人莊重的形象。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/maxresdefault-4-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fmaxresdefault-4-1024x576.jpg&h=838ec365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 藍可盈<br />\n<br />\n樣貌有幾分似陳慧琳的藍可盈，未做主播前，原來佢曾喺恆基地產做過公關，但因為唔適應，最後重返TVB重操故業。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/maxresdefault1-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fmaxresdefault1-1024x576.jpg&h=b97a4728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/af3062bfjw1e3dpvdj6glj-768x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Faf3062bfjw1e3dpvdj6glj-768x1024.jpg&h=0d384411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5. 周嘉儀<br />\n<br />\n人稱嘉儀bb的周嘉儀，退出新聞主播界後生活一樣多姿多采，不時喺佢facebook fan page更新動向。高登網友曾以「對腳真係世界級」的比喻來形容呢位前新聞主播，而唔知係咪人紅是非多，嘉儀bb曾被傳媒指控涉勾搭已婚無綫主播許方輝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/15192669_905720636196160_7396541391943681276_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F15192669_905720636196160_7396541391943681276_n.jpg&h=9f0dfb49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周嘉儀真係輕熟女中之典範！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mentalkhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/17834795_1019905898110966_972798185909791154_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalkhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F17834795_1019905898110966_972798185909791154_o.jpg&h=789bc29d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed3f0f2c1f4c48c49bbf9c712c9c201d05970761","tid":226378,"uid":111814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"居然冇大波寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b1cca34ab63919f063b2db77f9c511d92e599e","tid":226378,"uid":55603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7904a130581cc222589a363b2cac2acae54fab","tid":226378,"uid":55603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}